  ('description', '<p><b>Physical fitness</b> is a general state of <a title=\\"Health\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health\\">health</a> and well-being and, more specifically, the ability to perform aspects of <a title=\\"Outline of sports\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Outline_of_sports\\">sports</a> or occupations. Physical fitness is generally achieved through correct <a title=\\"Nutrition\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nutrition\\">nutrition</a>, moderate-vigorous physical activity, <a title=\\"Physical exercise\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_exercise\\">exercise</a> and rest.</p>', NULL, 'en-GB', 'category', 0, 19, NULL, NULL, NULL),
