  ('description', '<p>An <b>Internet forum</b>, or <b>message board</b>, is an <a class=\\"mw-redirect\\" title=\\"Online\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Online\\">online</a> discussion site where people can hold conversations in the form of posted messages. They differ from <a class=\\"mw-redirect\\" title=\\"Chat rooms\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chat_rooms\\">chat rooms</a> in that messages are often longer than one line of text, and are at least temporarily archived.</p>', NULL, 'en-GB', 'category', 0, 26, NULL, NULL, NULL),
