  ('description', '<p><b>Weather forecasting</b> is the application of science and technology to predict the state of the <a class=\\"mw-redirect\\" title=\\"Earth\\''s atmosphere\\" href=\\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Earth%27s_atmosphere\\">atmosphere</a> for a given location. Human beings have attempted to predict the weather informally for millennia, and formally since the nineteenth century.</p>', NULL, 'en-GB', 'category', 0, 30, NULL, NULL, NULL),
